---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base>
  <div style="margin-left: calc(2rem * 0" class="mastodon-comment">
    <div class="avatar">
      <a href="https://mstdn.party/@redintheshell" rel="nofollow">
        <img
          src="https://mastodon.me.uk/system/cache/accounts/avatars/109/541/491/696/600/028/original/6f5f42985b2ef664.jpeg"
        />
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mastodon-names">
      <a
        href="https://mstdn.party/@redintheshell"
        rel="nofollow"
        class="display-name">red</a
      >
      <a
        href="https://mstdn.party/@redintheshell"
        rel="nofollow"
        class="username"
      >
        @redintheshell@mstdn.party
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="toot-timestamp">
      <a
        href="https://mstdn.party/@redintheshell/109916409824577654"
        rel="nofollow">2023-02-23T22:28:32.000Z</a
      >
    </div>

    <div class="comment-content">
      <p>
        <span class="h-card">
          <a
            rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"
            class="u-url mention"
            href="https://mastodon.me.uk/@pikesley"
            >@<span>pikesley</span>
          </a>
        </span> ‘referential integrity’ and ‘hand-crafted yaml’ in the same sentence
        was sordid, but the entire journey was a sort of a mania.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="toot-stats">
      <span>
          <span class="mdi mdi-star"></span>1
        </span>
        <span>

            <span class="mdi mdi-repeat-variant"></span>0
        </span>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>

<style is:global>
  div.mastodon-comment {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-areas:
      "avatar mastodon-names"
      "avatar timestamp"
      "toot toot"
      "toot-stats toot-stats";
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 3fr;

    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    padding: 1rem;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  img {
    width: 20dvw;
  }

  div.avatar {
    grid-area: avatar;
  }

  div.mastodon-names {
    grid-area: mastodon-names;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: left;
    align-items: flex-end;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  a.username {
    display: none;
  }

  div.toot-timestamp {
    grid-area: timestamp;
  }

  div.mastodon-names, div.toot-timestamp, div.toot-stats {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  div.comment-content {
    grid-area: toot;
    margin: 0;
  }

  div.toot-stats {
    grid-area: toot-stats;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: right;
    column-gap: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
